TIME_SET_TICK_TOOLTIP: Sets the time beween each Tick
TIME_TICK_COUNT_TOOLTIP: Reports the number Ticks has passed since the last reset
TIME_TICKED_TOOLTIP: Returns true if the clock has ticked
TIME_CLEAR_TICK_TOOLTIP: Resets the tick counter and reset the tick clock
TIME_IF_TICKED_TOOLTIP: executes if the clock has ticked
